        "version_id": "CUNP",
        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "主人就誇獎這不義的管家做事聰明；因為今世之子，在世事之上，較比光明之子更加聰明。"
      },
      "esv": {
        "version_id": "ESV",
        "version_name": "English Standard Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "The master commended the dishonest manager for his shrewdness. For the sons of this world  are more shrewd in dealing with their own generation than the sons of light."
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "And his master praised the unrighteous manager because he had acted shrewdly; for the sons of this age are more shrewd in relation to their own kind than the sons of light."
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "“The master commended the dishonest manager because he had acted shrewdly. For the people of this world are more shrewd in dealing with their own kind than are the people of the light."
      },
      "nkjv": {
        "version_id": "NKJV",
        "version_name": "New King James Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "So the master commended the unjust steward because he had dealt shrewdly. For the sons of this world are more shrewd in their generation than the sons of light."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "“The rich man had to admire the dishonest rascal for being so shrewd. And it is true that the children of this world are more shrewd in dealing with the world around them than are the children of the light."
      }
